{
  "stem": "12150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And blockalteste, that's the older, barracks older it's translated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and he said to us, to me and a few more people, whatever they say, obey.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Otherwise, you'll be dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They could beat you to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They don't have to account for anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Or the blockalteste has a gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He can shoot you on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He doesn't have to account to his superiors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He doesn't have to mark your name, nothing, finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they did it, often, he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So if you want to be alive, that's what you have to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And-- something else he said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Wherever you go, if you have a chance to pick a commando-- commando is a type of work where you can steal food or clothing, a little more clothing for the winter.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "That's what-- if you have a chance, pick that, even if it's harder work, because what's the big deal with the light work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "If you have no food, you'll die anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "This way, you have a better chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they said, you speak to people that went through all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after six, seven days, I figure around seven days, we had an appell in the middle of the day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was unusual, so we already knew something was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like a 12 o'clock appell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They brought us bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not two slices-- gave everybody a half a loaf-- and more margarine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We already knew something good is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We already knew about the crematorium, about the-- the gas chambers in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, some prisoner showed us the-- the other end over there, that's where they burn the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what could we lose?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew it can only be better.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
